ct you when necessary.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully<br />\n<br />\niPOL Centre<br />\nfor Commissioner of Police<br />\n<br />\nThe following is a Chinese translation of the above message.<br />\nYou will not be able to read it unless you have a Chinese operating system : <br />\n_____________________________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n 多謝你聯絡香港警隊，我們會儘快處理你的來件。如有需要，我們會再聯絡你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n           警務處處長<br />\n<br />\n           （電子警察中心 代行）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等消息"},{"pid":"d9b3d5c0a3ccc73a324a52daa6b8a7112f917087","tid":405111,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"雖軟必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d7e8bdb7f0a008234ca435d50c816a55a3624d","tid":405111,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ceabe24a1662f7f07303917f921324fd3902a33","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推o既同時，真係不妨開個email (開個新o既都係一分鐘左右) ，寄出去畀啲壓力班慈母，睇下佢地個回應幾精彩都好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996b377f460a41085b647c060adc604458e26f6d","tid":405111,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>CAP 200 CRIMES ORDINANCE</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>Section 10 Offences</ins><br />\n<br />\n(1)Any person who&mdash;<br />\n(a)does or attempts to do, or makes any preparation to do, or conspires with any person to do, any act with a seditious intention; or<br />\n(b)utters any seditious words; or<br />\n(c)prints, publishes, sells, offers for sale, distributes, displays or reproduces any seditious publication; or<br />\n(d)imports any seditious publication, unless he has no reason to believe that it is seditious,<br />\nshall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable for a first offence to a fine of $5,000 and to imprisonment for 2 years, and for a subsequent offence to imprisonment for 3 years; and any seditious publication shall be forfeited to the Crown. (13 of 1938 s. 4 incorporated. Amended 22 of 1950 Schedule; 30 of 1970 s. 3)<br />\n<br />\n(2)Any person who without lawful excuse has in his possession any seditious publication shall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable for a first offence to a fine of $2,000 and to imprisonment for 1 year, and for a subsequent offence to imprisonment for 2 years; and such publication shall be forfeited to the Crown. (13 of 1938 s. 4 incorporated. Amended 22 of 1950 Schedule)<br />\n<br />\n(3)Where any person has been convicted of an offence under subsection (1) or (2) in respect of any seditious publication, the court may order the seizure and forfeiture of any copies of the seditious publication in the possession of&mdash;<br />\n(a)the person convicted; or<br />\n(b)any other person named in the order, if the court is satisfied by evidence on oath that the copies are in the possession of the other person for the use of the person convicted. (60 of 1971 s. 19 incorporated) [cf. 1819 c. 8 ss. 1 &amp; 2 U.K.]<br />\n<br />\n(4)Any copies seized under subsection (3) shall be disposed of as the court may direct; but no copies shall be destroyed until the expiration of the period within which an appeal may be lodged or, if an appeal is lodged, until the appeal has been finally determined or abandoned. (60 of 1971 s. 19 incorporated)<br />\n<br />\n(5)In this section&mdash;<br />\n&ldquo; seditious publication &rdquo; ( 煽動刊物 ) means a publication having a seditious intention;<br />\n&ldquo; seditious words &rdquo; ( 煽動文字 ) means words having a seditious intention. (13 of 1938 s. 2 incorporated)</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dce16cc52f3be80d0381e6b114f016e1cf8ca63d","tid":405111,"uid":107913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"好不安 SEND左"},{"pid":"2ec6273f38c7d0b280d5d82decb6e53753d6a155","tid":405111,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d807c6db5299233361af3511b973570a0b4ffda","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"驚畀人秋後算帳啲巴打唔洗擔心，呢篇文完全係撐政府同警方o既，咁都入撚得到，以後都唔洗屌人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊send啦，真係唔好忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6a3bcc7406d6e802d878e4f7f2ce6c24e5743a","tid":405111,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"乜戴耀廷搞港獨架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94a4c2c1da2d1c72b183afdf9c6a393d1bd1457","tid":405111,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n<br />\n5.串謀或唆使謀殺<br />\n<br />\n任何人在香港境內串謀、同謀及議同謀殺他人，以及在香港境內唆使、鼓勵、勸說、試圖勸說或建議別人謀殺他人，不論其謀殺對象屬何種國籍或具有何種公民身分或在任何地方，均屬犯罪，可處終身監禁。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>(由1911年第30號第2及5條修訂；由1983年第64號第4條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)<br />\n[比照 1861 c. 100 s. 4 U.K.]</strong></span>"},{"pid":"46257e82d5d011e1c523239591847895d57f96b2","tid":405111,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c31f68153e582daab9a1e1cd1474e88c3edf60","tid":405111,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n<br />\n5.串謀或唆使謀殺<br />\n<br />\n任何人在香港境內串謀、同謀及議同謀殺他人，以及在香港境內唆使、鼓勵、勸說、試圖勸說或建議別人謀殺他人，不論其謀殺對象屬何種國籍或具有何種公民身分或在任何地方，均屬犯罪，可處終身監禁。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>(由1911年第30號第2及5條修訂；由1983年第64號第4條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)<br />\n[比照 1861 c. 100 s. 4 U.K.]</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def02c553855ff44ad2e015e4333092e7e890f6c","tid":405111,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"以及在香港境內唆使、鼓勵、勸說、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>試圖勸說或建議別人</strong></span>謀殺他人，不論其謀殺對象屬何種國籍或具有何種公民身分或在任何地方，均屬犯罪，可處終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n試圖同建議都計<br />\n何妖今次仲有得走？？"},{"pid":"d22bfb7d842f026b6bc14791a5fab381db2f4c74","tid":405111,"uid":93351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人比埋律師/大律師公會睇下有冇違返律師守則<br />\n另立法會有冇得投訴?<br />\n有冇議員守則可以DQ到?"},{"pid":"7048a4afdfabe0ccee2fd592f993c1ece98dccf9","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人比埋律師/大律師公會睇下有冇違返律師守則<br />\n另立法會有冇得投訴?<br />\n有冇議員守則可以DQ到?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟整咗個律師會版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n致香港律師會負責人:<br />\n<br />\n\t本人於二零一七年九月十七日，於甚具公信力之星島日報得悉前香港律師會會長何君堯先生曾於當日下午之公眾集會期間，涉嫌公然教唆及煽動公眾對討論香港獨立議題之人士「殺無赦」。以警方統計數字，當日與會人數達二千一百人，實為公眾聚集。而於公眾聚集中使用恐嚇性言詞如「殺無赦」，意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧，何君堯先生已涉嫌干犯公安條例第17 B條，而本人亦從星島日報及其他傳媒報導中，得知何君堯先生所提及之「殺」，應為傳統意義上之謀殺，本人現引述星島日報及明報之報導<br />\n<br />\n星島日報<br />\n何君堯則在電台節目反駁，要求港獨等同戰爭，「在戰爭中殺敵人有何問題？」<br />\n<br />\n明報<br />\n立法會議員何君堯昨日發起集會，要求港大開除法律系副教授戴耀廷，以及反港獨，其間站台的屏山鄉事委員會主席曾樹和高叫提倡港獨者應「殺」，何君堯即和應說「無赦」，更指「（搞港獨）啲人唔殺咗佢做咩」<br />\n<br />\n引文來源<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.singtao.com.au/8-香港/172471-稱搞港獨可殺或違《公安條例》\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com.au%2F8-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F172471-%E7%A8%B1%E6%90%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E5%8F%AF%E6%AE%BA%E6%88%96%E9%81%95%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B&d=UzWHiFDZ68nYT9RT6v2vL8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0a00d90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.singtao.com.au/8-香港/172471-稱搞港獨可殺或違《公安條例》</a>　何君堯：有何問題？戴耀廷：促警方執法/<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505704670720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505704670720&d=UzWHiFDZ68nYT9RT6v2vL8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0422a4f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505704670720&h=a83f0c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505704670720</a><br />\n&emsp;<br />\n\t從何先生當日所指之殺無赦，及其後以戰爭中殺敵為喻，可見何先生涉嫌有意煽動社會公眾如戰爭中使用暴力，謀殺討論港獨之人士。此一行為亦極可能干犯&lt;&lt;刑事罪行條例&gt;&gt; 第10條，同時亦涉及干犯公安條例第245章第26條。<br />\n\t何先生作為執業律師及前香港律師會會長，一言一行均極受公眾關注，而根據《律師執業規則》規定，任何律師在執業為律師的過程中，不得作出或准許他人代他作出任何危及或損害或相當可能危及或損害以下各項的事情─<br />\n(a) 他的獨立性或正直品格；<br />\n(b) 任何人延聘他所選擇律師的自由；<br />\n(c) 他為當事人的最佳利益而行事的職責；<br />\n(d) 他的個人名譽或律師專業的名譽；<br />\n(e) 適當的工作標準；或<br />\n(f) 他對法院的職責。<br />\n<br />\n而何君堯先生所提出之言論，極有可能已干犯(d)，因其於公眾集會中公然鼓吹殺人之涉嫌犯法之行為，與其及後之殺豬殺狗言論，必會給予公眾一個極壞印象。令公眾以為身為律師仍可如此公然宣揚低俗言論，遇事訴諸暴力而非法律。此等行為相當可能危及其個人名譽及律師專業之名譽，本人現謹此投訴。"},{"pid":"db43886e0977a342e29d224bcd36805cd5c27484","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五毛你係得o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f487ea7dd527a2a111179705482cd0a797b3c115","tid":405111,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"done<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edc1c9c28dfa065ecefea2999eee15a50fa05d9","tid":405111,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"已send <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52a92b60a0f05daa7518b733629d1d9903c8aa7","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"審 查 及 紀 律 部 下 設 兩 個 小 組 ： 登 記 組 處 理 事 務 律 師 執 業 認 可 程 序 ， 發 出 週 年 執 業 證 書 ， 替 實 習 律 師 及 外 地 律 師 登 記 ； 而 執 業 操 守 組 則 調 查 有 關 專 業 操 守 不 當 行 為 的 投 訴 。 <br />\n<br />\n董 彥 嘉\t審 查 及 紀 律 部 總 監<br />\n嚴 慧 雯\t執 業 操 守 部 副 總 監<br />\n廖 詠 賢\t註 冊 部 副 總 監<br />\n<br />\n查 詢 :\t請 聯 絡:<br />\n審 查 及 紀 律 部 的 工 作\tdofc@hklawsoc.org.hk\t電 話 : (852) 2846 0561<br />\n有 關 專 業 操 守 事 務\tcomplaints@hklawsoc.org.hk\t電 話 : (852) 2846 0535<br />\n認 可 資 格 及 註 冊\tregist@hklawsoc.org.hk\t電 話 : (852) 2846 0527"},{"pid":"bea8e6c7602d1e91160f94396055b675ae0ae01f","tid":405111,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好不安同憤怒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我一諗返我個user name，就覺得好不安，生命受到威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家真係一齊寄啦，呢封野係支持香港政府同讚揚警方的，咁樣都有風險，以後真係街都唔撚好出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢件事要認真對待<br />\n就好似教大poster單野咁<br />\n要真誠地感到不安及憤怒</blockquote>"},{"pid":"be4e3de42a420ded3c4c76d613a895f66c7bcba0","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好不安同憤怒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我一諗返我個user name，就覺得好不安，生命受到威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家真係一齊寄啦，呢封野係支持香港政府同讚揚警方的，咁樣都有風險，以後真係街都唔撚好出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢件事要認真對待<br />\n就好似教大poster單野咁<br />\n要真誠地感到不安及憤怒</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我係真誠地不安同憤怒的，唔係都唔洗打咁大篇文去投訴佢。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好希望香港仲有法治，但你日日見到班高官仲有律政司搬龍門o既嘴臉，有時真係好撚心寒，唯有盡自己一分力去反抗吧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88579d692112553b84c3ea6a4a62e04fa988e334","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"各位巴打，如果你曾經有為過呢啲不公而憤怒，曾經有諗過要呢啲人講完呢種涼薄冷血說話後得到應有懲罰，其中一樣你可以做o既就係試下send封投訴信出去。係，好可能唔會得到咩回報，但勿以善少而不為。我就幫各位巴打準備好樣本了，只要稍作修改就可以send出去，各位巴打請幫手，唔會阻大家好耐的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d689115b0b463899b2a8cca289973c74dc91c89b","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fabd9d10f47c280fc0122a3e4d0b0a86ec488f5","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7a4d7a635566b6f3b231aa248f9543732caa7a","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"用力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b376f0bf89653cee6ff38f897089e4bb7c18fac","tid":405111,"uid":137504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco