ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d90800c9ad7d4a6f0bdaae0ec5c18a4cdc3d7f","tid":405111,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【香港法律】唆使、鼓勵、勸說、試圖勸說或建議別人謀殺他人，可處終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n<br />\n<ins>5. 串謀或唆使謀殺</ins><br />\n<br />\n任何人在香港境內串謀、同謀及議同謀殺他人，以及在香港境內唆使、鼓勵、勸說、試圖勸說或建議別人謀殺他人，不論其謀殺對象屬何種國籍或具有何種公民身分或在任何地方，均屬犯罪，可處終身監禁。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(由1911年第30號第2及5條修訂；由1983年第64號第4條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)<br />\n[比照 1861 c. 100 s. 4 U.K.]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405254\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405254</a></span>"},{"pid":"d3409e20514be55e3b6739969432f214b89ae28a","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"因曾自稱社會工作者及於法庭自拍後再揚言對港獨人士殺無赦而遭廣大市民報警舉報涉嫌犯罪及被投訴違反律師專業守則之香港律師會前會長何君堯先生, 你而家係唔係仲想殺無赦啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e00b21ac1e247b52be279c246c8e7180c923eda","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"差警方未覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過好似已經有人報案成功了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79e814ddbda5b7b7f9c4aa61909a87d1df18e02","tid":405111,"uid":34144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:57:28.000Z","msg":"大家要學習雲海大師，凡事有理就投訴到盡o既精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b6e1bb9e4566817d2dfa3039be88e4a6fec242","tid":405111,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:57:31.00